Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PA·I·NA·TSU·PU·RU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭 剪刀 布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 規定好了一次一個台階的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GU·RI·KO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的 附贈品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼隨便加東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？我就是加了個普普通通的「附贈品」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 這樣也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你要是這麼來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也啟動我自己的規則了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 接下來是麻衣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHI·YO·TA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NI·KE·RA·HA·TO·HO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RA·SU·TE·NO·HA·TE·KI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RA·TO·NA·RI·HA·SHI·TE·TO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 媽媽 不是跟你說了7點叫我起床的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\bord0\shad0\c&H212122&\frz30.555\pos(291,351)}美\N緒
