Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\bord0\shad0\c&H212122&\frz30.555\pos(194,488)}踢\N籐\N球\N去\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs33\bord0\shad0\c&H212122&\frz30.555\pos(183,614)}媽\N媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}町內會：類似於國內的街道委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐 籐球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還是值日生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧鐘也是 為什麼偏偏今天沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒電了就事先告訴我一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個白癡傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}スカポンタン：1976《時間飛船》裡大姐頭約尼訓斥部下的經典台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 以最後一圈的速度衝刺的話 說不定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個可怕的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像 來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個短跑員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 在 追我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:05:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個木魚 是你掉的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金木魚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做點什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的時候是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而有的時候也是 熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的真面目是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:06:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘 正確答案是姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著美緒的校服所以不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就能見到如此精湛的螺旋突刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很出色的一擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 我也很辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關掉鬧鐘也費了很大勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你是犯人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別別 別那麼生氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 用這些錢請你吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}野口：野口英世 一千日元紙幣上的頭像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的野口！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHI·YO·TA
