Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\bord0\shad0\c&HE2E2E2&\pos(640,410)}咒語錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鯊魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯊魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 博士你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 那片雲朵 好像鯊魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.62,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 哪一片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你買來了哦 牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}註釋：特濃4.5是牛奶產品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 4.5 4.5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs39}吶 牛奶 4.5 牛奶 4.5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 特濃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼了 突然想喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有瑞士捲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你怎麼隨便改造啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有瑞士捲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃 4.5牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼4.5啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得手腕裡帶著瑞士捲生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼涼的真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 出去了要是這副樣子被別人看到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 咕嚕咕嚕咕嚕 咕嚕嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我也想吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞士捲我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那名乃就來點小甜麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 按錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就 就說了為什麼要做這種東西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得要是因為內部原因在外面啟動了的話會怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}徒手格鬥專家太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs39\blur2}對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}啊 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂播放機能也想加上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼變成改造方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請仔細聽著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小甜麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你都已經吃了瑞士捲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便吧 反正還有年輪蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 這次會從哪裡出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面？ 下面？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請一開始就全都放在冰箱裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭 接下來是布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出力量 石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美～緒～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 滿臉笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筆記給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道作業又忘做了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真是難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這樣的話考試又會吃苦頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次 就這一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一次了 拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐 之前也這麼說來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫一言既出駟馬難追！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 都說了你已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這一次了哦 真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 該帶的東西就是美緒你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐 剛才說的東西完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣 抄完了馬上還給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼 給我看看給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 感覺我好像忘了什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上 做完作業之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完作業之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像畫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像畫了什麼畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了擦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs39}那樣不行哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才忘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我也忘了寫作業了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真是頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 筆記先還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 你看了也沒什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了下一次我會自己做的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了啊 這下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種畫要是被看見了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會被投來奇怪的眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且會看到那幅畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的傳播速度可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音速！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本 是語文的筆記哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數學的是這本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這本 上面寫著數學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子好疼啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就會抄完的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被看到了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的高中生活就
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐 那本筆記！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我花一千日元買下來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼跑掉了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本筆記…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本筆記…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會爆炸的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本跑不過小祐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生要 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有點不快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總的來說 是很幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生要完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男人們的盛宴一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樣子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:52.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\pos(588,473)\c&H4C4C57&}椰\N\N果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}西班牙語：Nata De Coco
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 還是夠不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 從後面把筆記傳上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後忘了寫作業的傢伙趕緊報上名來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一時不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好在平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來我平穩的日常就能夠回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有擦掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 長野原
