Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安中同學 有時間麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
