Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 那個髮帶 是不是有點太大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔兔 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小甜麵包也很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
